Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom threw you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She threw you away like trash, along\Nwith that drunk dad of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever leave this trash dump again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.91,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(269,100)\pos(365,350)}The Town of Slaughter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you mind getting out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to drink, pay off your tab first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to serve to someone\Nwho takes the money his son worked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about the incident with Mr. Konrad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was the one who shot Mrs. Hillman's dog, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the guts to fire a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a drunken coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to search in this rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Merkel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should call it off, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Merkel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merkel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merkel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is Laufer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please respond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your gun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.17,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the guts to fire a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.18,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.06,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a drunken coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are dead bodies strewn all over town...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Wim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let go of the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot them, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kept teasing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to calm down and remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you this gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you got here with that leg, Laufer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Call the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone lines are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He took my gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an outsider I've never seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's apply first aid, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many of your friends have come to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did manage to spread quite\Na few guns around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even gave one to a child like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You aren't trash."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't take them seriously."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There was a reason you were born."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you've been encouraging him by saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't fire the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the bullets are still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim kept to what you taught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of you, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the town is full of dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many did you distribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many guns did you distribute in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people took guns from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me any angrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible will happen if you make me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked just like our grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked just like our grandson who passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew a lot about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just like our grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were writing a letter to your dead grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were passing on information to "him."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His target is probably me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mr. Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.00,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The heavy rain that has been falling in southern Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.73,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,...has caused significant amount of damage to Bayern.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.36,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The state has raised its warning level to grade four...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're smoking too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.99,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,as the damage continues to mount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? At least I quit drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should quit smoking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Does it look like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd turn that over to the police next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys don't believe the important details.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this is the man I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he has gone by himself to kill a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma will come back, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.01,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here is the reported damage for each area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.30,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the flooding of the Elgar River, several places are blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.10,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the railroad is out of service in both directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:08.02,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Now because several locations have no power,\Nit's difficult to make phone calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received this letter three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After consulting with Dr. Gillen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've decided that we shouldn't hide it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Nina."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll be waiting for you in Ruhenheim."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told us before what Johan is trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "perfect suicide," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as how numerous innocent people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruhenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a country town in southern\NGermany with that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance that Tenma went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very strange feeling that I'm getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought you were just a character\Nfrom a certain person's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just like the characters that\Nappear in your picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For years, I've been carrying out my investigations\Nby collecting objective data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this time, I completely ignored the data\Nand purely followed that man's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I followed the clues, partially for my own amusement...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met a young man who had entered the Red\NRose Mansion many times in Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This postcard you sent him with a hand-drawn picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under your real name, Klaus Poppe, signed K. P.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after arriving at this location...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and seeing you with my own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if a character from a storybook\Nhas escaped from its pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the list of names I had researched of\Npeople who escaped Czechoslovakia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the name "Klaus Poppe" was indeed on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right before the Berlin Wall fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you fled to this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you running from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511 was created in East\NGermany based upon your concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was created there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to run away from people like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the young man named Johan is trying to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's exactly what's happening to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another gunshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ton of people were dead on the way to this hotel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is happening to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry and take me away from this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roads have been closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming and going from the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And every time you come back, you take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick from the gunpowder and the smell\Nof blood that's covering the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered a hot cup of tea from the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will have disappeared\Nby the time the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some conditions if you're going to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Gillen must go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get ready to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, please hurry and do what we just discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter and Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Mr. Schuwald, Karl, and Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who knows Johan should go into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is trying to erase all the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry! Before Dieter notices!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of you, Dr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of Karl and Lotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of the Fortners...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have many memories that I don't want to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have memories that I do want to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your memories with Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not erase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A police officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His gun has been taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,save the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're shooting... all over town...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, several armed men came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, even the townspeople picked up guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and started shooting each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have to call for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save... the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I heard that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was in 1995.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was during the testimony of a certain neurosurgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're admitting that your deduction was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is still an important reference for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is just a fictional character to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fictional character...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the words that captivated\Nme during my vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a real man become a fictional character?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people who know him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people who know his past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone must be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And ultimately, it'll become like the ending\Nto one of your books, Mr. Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though he now had a name, there was\Nno one left to call him by his name."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Johan."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It is a wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what's happening in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Johan, that's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a fictional character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a man named Neumaier\Nwho signed the hotel registry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor am I Wolfgang Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's disappear together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the man who \N stole my memories and my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was here, simply waiting for my sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't know how I can atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to accept\Nwhatever happens here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not afraid to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what kind of sin you've committed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what it means to destroy\Nthe boundary between good and evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what happens to people\Nif you awaken the monster inside them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People have to think of food as delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to enjoy a picnic on a holiday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to think a beer after work tastes great...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People feel sad from the bottoms of their\Nhearts when their children pass away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you away from this town,\Nand I'll publicize everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show the world the identity\Nof the monster that you've awoken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's a man who's controlling this massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm not carrying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to leave the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to the entrance of the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you all run?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There is a man giving orders in Hotel Bergbach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is the only gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two were outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened because I won the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had only told someone sooner\Nabout Konrad's dead body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the entire town went crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I haven't fired a single shot yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow this one and this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You protect this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even ordinary townspeople are carrying guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this job is done, let me buy you a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A delicious beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:31.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.47,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:34.43,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
